des:
This Alexa skill is designed and built by Vivian(Weixian ) Wu. She sees herself as a communication leader, so named the skill Commleader Vivian, and it's also the invoke name on all Amazon Alexa devices (for example Amazon Dot, Amazon Echo, and etc.). After you wake up this skill, simply begin by asking Alexa “who is Vivian”, and you will be able to receive information about Vivian, including her educational background, work experience, skill sets, and also her life story that shows her core values.

Vivian is obsessive about emerging technologies and believes its power in changing people’s future life. By taking the chance to design and develop this skill, Vivian was able to learn and practice some AI programming skill and excel the knowledge she acquired from the communication leadership class. She enjoys interacting with the skill and hope you all do! If you have any comments or suggestions, please feel free to contact her. Her email address is weixianwu1994@gmail.com. She will be more willing to listen to people’s voices and make this skill better!
